are they?

154
00:08:01,117 --> 00:08:02,818
<i>Well, neither are
you when you're hungry.</i>

155
00:08:02,853 --> 00:08:04,487
<i>I don't suppose</i>
<i>you've fed them.</i>

156
00:08:04,521 --> 00:08:06,456
<i>No, I can't say I have.</i>

157
00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:09,259
<i>You didn't pack any lion's</i>
<i>milk for me before I left.</i>

158
00:08:09,293 --> 00:08:12,529
