159
00:08:12,563 --> 00:08:15,299
You're going to get in trouble.

160
00:08:15,333 --> 00:08:17,568
Want some?

161
00:08:19,303 --> 00:08:21,071
Sure.
What the hell.

162
00:08:26,311 --> 00:08:28,278
<i>Come on.</i>

163
00:08:33,585 --> 00:08:35,719
- Hello.
- Hi.

164
00:08:35,754 --> 00:08:37,688
<i>But why don't they?</i>

165
00:08:37,722 --> 00:08:39,356
<i>It's at least two days</i>
<i>since they've eaten.</i>

166
00:08:39,391 --> 00:08:41,024
- <i>They'll just die.</i>
- <i>Yes, I know.</i>

167
00:08:41,059 --> 00:08:43,427
<i>It must be the formula.</i>
<i>We haven't hit on it yet.</i>

168
00:08:43,462 --> 00:08:45,329
<i>We'll just have try again.</i>

169
00:08:45,364 --> 00:08:47,899
<i>Right, back to</i>
<i>the drawing board.</i>

170
00:08:47,933 --> 00:08:50,201
<i>Formula...</i>
- <i>13.</i>

