And I said no,
you're not coming in.

185
00:10:14,487 --> 00:10:15,988
'Cause you don't want
I should see you?

186
00:10:16,022 --> 00:10:17,757
<i>You see me at home,</i>
<i>for Christ's sake.</i>

187
00:10:17,792 --> 00:10:19,526
You stare at me
when I'm sleeping.

188
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:21,194
Eh, I don't want
to see you anyway.

189
00:10:21,229 --> 00:10:23,163
- I just want to use the photocopy.
- For what?

190
00:10:23,198 --> 00:10:25,766
I'm building my case.

191
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,834
Again?

192
00:10:27,869 --> 00:10:29,570
Who's this?

193
